{"tid":1404823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日尖沙咀嘅姐姐多謝你","createTime":"2019-08-04T06:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:14:43.000Z","uid":124824,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"65369c5a2a8d0068d5546e1d15e8c1d9a10aa3cc","tid":1404823,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:14:43.000Z","msg":"代post:<br />\n<br />\n琴日係油麻地行緊去尖沙咀方向<br />\n我帶緊對冰袖個時有一位姐姐行咗過嚟 <br />\n比咗幾張嘢我同我朋友<br />\n當時我有啲反應唔嚟 <br />\n所以唔記得咗講多謝你<br />\n雖然唔知你會唔會上連登<br />\n但容許我係到同你講翻聲多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時想比大家知道<br />\n仲有好多人默默咁用行動去幫助我地<br />\n大家唔可以放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n紙入面包住咗張八達通有$300係入面<br />\n你地嘅心意唔捨得用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wvcY4hz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwvcY4hz.png&h=5a9cd7e5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}